<html>
<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
chat [message] : send [message] to the mud general chatter channel<br>
chat [on|off]  : turn chat on or off<br>
chat           : display last 10 chats<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
 Use this channel for idle talk about anything you want, but please<br>
stay in character, of course.  If trying to get the attention of an<br>
immortal use gossip.  Use of this channel requires gossip points; it<br>
costs one gossip point per use of chat.  These points accumulate over<br>
time, and non-use of any channel.  To see how many points your character<br>
has accumulated, type "score"; the points are listed under Gsp_points.<br>
<br>
See also: channels, score<br>
</html>
</body>
